videos.description: No. 2 overall pick James Wiseman gets his first NBA bucket as he goes baseline for the jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Wiseman’s first bucket is a dunk) 2020/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wiseman's first bucket is a dunk

videos.description: Kevin Durant doesn't miss a beat as he scores a quick eight points, hitting his first three shots from the field.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (KD starts out hot, hits first three shots) 2020/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: KD starts out hot, hits first three shots

videos.description: Kevin Durant goes right by the defense and flushes it home with two hands.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (KD goes baseline for the jam) 2020/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: KD goes baseline for the jam

videos.description: Kelly Oubre Jr. soars way up above the rim for the huge putback dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Oubre skies for the monster putback jam) 2020/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oubre skies for the monster putback jam

videos.description: Steph Curry comes off the screen and lobs it to James Wiseman who calmly finishes at the rim.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Steph, Wiseman combine for bucket) 2020/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Steph, Wiseman combine for bucket

videos.description: Kyrie Irving shakes Brad Wanamaker for the impressive layup and then later in the quarter he knocks down the difficult fadeaway over the outstretched arm of James Wiseman.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kyrie uses all his skills on two impressive second-quarter buckets) 2020/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kyrie uses all his skills on two impressive second-quarter buckets

videos.description: Kyrie Irving walks into the long 3-pointer from way behind the line as time in the first half expires.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kyrie knocks down long 3 right before the half) 2020/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kyrie knocks down long 3 right before the half

videos.description: Kevin Durant throws it up to DeAndre Jordan who emphatically slams it home and lets out a scream.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Jordan fired up after throwing down lob from Durant) 2020/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jordan fired up after throwing down lob from Durant

videos.description: Kevin Durant gets out in transition and flies toward the rim for the easy dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (KD soars to the rim for a transition dunk) 2020/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: KD soars to the rim for a transition dunk

videos.description: James Wiseman uses his whole skill set as he knocks down a 3, sinks a midrange jumper and throws down an alley-oop dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Wiseman has impressive stretch in fourth quarter) 2020/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wiseman has impressive stretch in fourth quarter

videos.description: Kevin Durant and Kyrie Irving combine for 48 points as the Nets dominate the Warriors 125-99 on opening night.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (KD, Kyrie cook Golden State on opening night) 2020/12/22 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: KD, Kyrie cook Golden State on opening night

videos.description: Steph Curry jokingly says it was "awful" playing against Kevin Durant again but it was great to see him recover from his injury the way he did.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Steph jokes about playing KD again: It was 'awful') 2020/12/22

videos.headline: Steph jokes about playing KD again: It was 'awful'

videos.description: Kevin Durant goes in depth on why he says he doesn't need to prove he's a top two or three player again as he knows he has a full skillset as a player.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (KD doesn’t feel he needs to prove he’s a top 2 or 3 player) 2020/12/22

videos.headline: KD doesn't feel he needs to prove he's a top 2 or 3 player
